Cristina Marcos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristina_Marcos 0 Cristina Marcos (born 19 December 1963) is a Spanish actress. She has appeared in over 35 films and television shows since 1981. She starred in the 1981 film Maravillas, which was entered into the 31st Berlin International Film Festival. Cristina_Marcos ( born 19_December_1963 ) is a_Spanish_actress .
